issue_title: Correct navigation bar for some resolution
Add support with Dice So Nice
issue_body:
Summary:
Dice So Nice is a popular module that supports custom sides (as seen on Alien RPG). I should look into how to configure Dice So Nice with my system to show the vtm icon on d10 sides

Acceptance Criteria:
- Dice So Nice is configured to match rolls generated by character sheet
- Dice So Nice shows sides matching icons

https://www.notion.so/Weird-Database-Things-eeb860803c914f098b7ae7294e6644c0

- [ ] Some userCourses (mainly TA's) have a null user id
- [ ] Null Semester IDs in course_model (addressed in #465)

**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe:** HungerGames Gamelistener currently high CPU usage sometimes when end the HungerGames game. **Describe the solution you'd like:** Optimize HungerGames Gamelistener.
